{
  "texts": [
    "In the gold knowledge scenario, we directly feed the model with the ground truth documents.",
    "This serves as an upper bound for RAG.",
    "Additionally, this strategy allows us to study the ability of the techniques to incorporate knowledge in the responses.",
    "We select the widely-used 7B version of Llama2 C and Mistral I as base models.",
    "For in-context learning, we experiment with three instructions for each dialogue type and select the best based on the development set performance."
  ]
}